name: Love is Power
description:
#9
When you connect to your Love, you are a powerful being, and I am not talking about the love for someone. I am talking about your inner unconditional Love for yourself and life.

Piece #9 of the collection:
I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art

The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth.
